[0.000, "o", "                                                                                                              \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m- [[2021-08-03]] The Language Instinct, by Steven Pinker\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                         \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m- [[2021-08-03]] If sophisticated domain experts don’t understand the model, there is something wrong with the model.\u001b[39m                                                                                                            \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m- [[2021-08-03]] The essential principle is that any element of a layer depends only on other elements in the same layer or on elements of the layers “beneath” it. Communication upward must pass through some indire"]
[0.000, "o", "ct\u001b[39m         \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mmechanism,\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m-\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m[[2021-08-03]] An object defined primarily by its identity is called an ENTITY.1 ENTITIES have special modeling and design considerations. They have life cycles that can radically change their form and content, but a\u001b[39m       \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mthread of continuity must be maintained.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                       \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b"]
[0.000, "o", "[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m-\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m[[2021-08-03]] An object that represents a descriptive aspect of the domain with no conceptual identity is called a VALUE OBJECT. VALUE OBJECTS are instantiated to represent elements of the design that we care about only\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mfor what they are, not who or which they are.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                  \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m-\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m[[2021-08-03]] A SERVICE is an operation offered as an interface that stands alone in the model, without encapsulating state, as ENTITIES and VALUE OBJECTS do. SERVICES are a common pattern in technical frameworks, but\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m"]
[0.001, "o", "█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mthey can also apply in the domain layer.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                       \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m- [[2021-08-03]] A good SERVICE has three characteristics. 1. The operation relates to a domain concept that is not a natural part of an ENTITY or VALUE OBJECT. 2. The interface is defined in terms of other elements of the\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mdomain model. 3. The operation is stateless.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[2m---\u001b[2"]
[0.000, "o", "2m                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[2m---\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mFile: working/idx_team/Reading List.md\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                            \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mRelevance: 1.2762482166290283\u001b[39m                                 "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                                                                                                                    \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mContent: - \u001b[3mThe Why:\u001b[23m The science of delivery. It provides the evidence for which metrics (DORA) actually move the needle for developer velocity.\u001b[39m                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[2m---\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m╰────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[0.000, "o", "───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;196;167;231m✦ \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mBased on your notes, here is a synthesized framework for your article on developer productivity in the age of LLMs and coding agents:\u001b[39m                                                                                              \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                              "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                       \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m1. The New Productivity Bottleneck: Information Discovery\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                          \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mThe primary source of friction for engineering teams has shifted. While technical debt was once the top concern, the \u001b[1mAtlassian State of Developer Experience 2025\u001b[22m report indicates that \u001b[1mfinding information\u001b[22m is now the #1 \"time\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244msuck.\"\u001b[39m                                                       "]
