[0.082, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[1;1H\u001b[47B\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m⠧\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;196;167;231mMapping Agent Applications\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m(esc to cancel, 15s)\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                     \r\n\u001b[7B\u001b[52;4H\u001b[?2026l"]
[0.040, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[1;1H\u001b[47B\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m⠧\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;196;167;231mMapping Agent Applications\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m(esc to cancel, 16s)\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                     \r\n\u001b[7B\u001b[52;4H\u001b[?2026l"]
[0.035, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[1;1H\u001b[47B\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m⠇\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;196;167;231mMapping Agent Applications\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m(esc to cancel, 16s)\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                     \r\n\u001b[7B\u001b[52;4H\u001b[?2026l"]
[0.050, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[1;1H\u001b[3B\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mmechanism,\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m-\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m[[2021-08-03]] An object defined primarily by its identity is called an ENTITY.1 ENTITIES have special modeling and design considerations. They have life cycles that can radically change their form and content, but a\u001b[39m       \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mthread of continuity must be maintained.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                       \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m-\u001b[39m \u001b[3"]
[0.000, "o", "8;2;224;222;244m[[2021-08-03]] An object that represents a descriptive aspect of the domain with no conceptual identity is called a VALUE OBJECT. VALUE OBJECTS are instantiated to represent elements of the design that we care about only\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mfor what they are, not who or which they are.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                  \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m-\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m[[2021-08-03]] A SERVICE is an operation offered as an interface that stands alone in the model, without encapsulating state, as ENTITIES and VALUE OBJECTS do. SERVICES are a common pattern in technical frameworks, but\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mthey can also apply in the domain layer.\u001b[39m               "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                                                                                                                        \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m- [[2021-08-03]] A good SERVICE has three characteristics. 1. The operation relates to a domain concept that is not a natural part of an ENTITY or VALUE OBJECT. 2. The interface is defined in terms of other elements of the\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mdomain model. 3. The operation is stateless.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[2m---\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                          "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                     \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[2m---\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mFile: working/idx_team/Reading List.md\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                            \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mRelevance: 1.2762482166290283\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[38"]
[0.000, "o", ";2;224;222;244mContent: - \u001b[3mThe Why:\u001b[23m The science of delivery. It provides the evidence for which metrics (DORA) actually move the needle for developer velocity.\u001b[39m                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \u001b[2m---\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[0.000, "o", "──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[38;2;196;167;231m✦ \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mBased on your notes, here is a synthesized framework for your article on developer productivity in the age of LLMs and coding agents:\u001b[39m                                                                                               \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;22"]
[0.000, "o", "4;222;244m1. The New Productivity Bottleneck: Information Discovery\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                           \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mThe primary source of friction for engineering teams has shifted. While technical debt was once the top concern, the \u001b[1mAtlassian State of Developer Experience 2025\u001b[22m report indicates that \u001b[1mfinding information\u001b[22m is now the #1 \"time\u001b[39m     \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244msuck.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                              \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m*\u001b[39m \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244mArticle Angle:\u001b[22m Coding agents aren't just for writing functions; their greatest productivity impact may be as intelligent retrieval layers that solve the information discovery problem, all"]
[0.000, "o", "owing developers to bypass the\u001b[39m        \r\n     \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mfriction of navigating fragmented documentation and legacy codebases.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                            \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m2. Agents as Standardization Engines\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                     "]
[0.000, "o", "                          \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mYour notes on \"core concepts\" highlight that agents provide:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                       \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mDomain Expertise:\u001b[22m Specialized agents (Go, Security, DevOps) provide deep knowledge on demand.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mTeam Standardization:\u001b[22m Using a \"senior reviewer\" agent ensures that every developer—regardless of experience—is measured against the same standards and best practices.\u001b[39m                                                          \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mConsistent Voice:\u001b[22m Reducing the cognitive load of switching between different sty"]
[0.000, "o", "les or behavioral constraints.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                  \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m3. Controlling Complexity with Domain-Driven Design (DDD)\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                          \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mThe complexity of modern softw"]
[0.000, "o", "are is still the greatest hurdle. As highlighted in your \u001b[3mDomain-Driven Design\u001b[23m notes:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                 \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mLeverage through Models:\u001b[22m LLMs can help developers brainstorm and experiment with domain models more rapidly.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                    \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m*\u001b[39m \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244mConscious Knowledge Growth:\u001b[22m Highly productive teams grow their knowledge consciously. Agents can act as the \"memory\" of a team, distilling brainstorming sessions into a \"knowledge-rich model\" that binds the domain to the\u001b[39m    \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n     \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mcode.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                         "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                  \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m4. Measuring What Matters (DORA Metrics)\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                           \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mTo move beyond hype, productivity must be grounded in the \"science of delivery.\"\u001b[39m                            "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                                                                       \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mArticle Angle:\u001b[22m Use DORA metrics (from \u001b[3mThe Why\u001b[23m) to evaluate if AI tools are actually moving the needle on velocity and stability, rather than just increasing the volume of code produced\u001b[39m                                        \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[9B\u001b[52;4H\u001b[?2026l"]
