[0.000, "o", "                                                                                 \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mYour notes on \"core concepts\" highlight that agents provide:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                        \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mDomain Expertise:\u001b[22m Specialized agents (Go, Security, DevOps) provide deep knowledge on demand.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                    \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mTeam Standardization:\u001b[22m Using a \"senior reviewer\" agent ensures that every developer—regardless of experience—is measured against the same standards and best practices.\u001b[39m                                                           \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mConsistent Voice:\u001b[22m Reducing the cognitive load of switching between different styles or behavioral constraints.\u001b[39m   "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                                                                \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n\u001b[E  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m3. Controlling Complexity with Domain-Driven Design (DDD)\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                           \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mThe complexity of modern software is still the greatest hurdle. As highlighted in your \u001b[3mDomain-Driven Design\u001b[23m notes:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                  \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mLeverage through Models:\u001b[22m LLMs can help developers brainstorm and experiment with domain models more rapidly.\u001b[39"]
[0.000, "o", "m                                                                                                                     \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m*\u001b[39m \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244mConscious Knowledge Growth:\u001b[22m Highly productive teams grow their knowledge consciously. Agents can act as the \"memory\" of a team, distilling brainstorming sessions into a \"knowledge-rich model\" that binds the domain to the\u001b[39m     \r\n     \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mcode.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n                                                                                                                               "]
[0.000, "o", "                                                                                                       \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m4. Measuring What Matters (DORA Metrics)\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                           \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mTo move beyond hype, productivity must be grounded in the \"science of delivery.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mArticle Angle:\u001b[22m Use DORA metrics (from \u001b[3mThe Why\u001b[23m) to evaluate if AI tools are actually moving the needle on velocity and stability, rather than just increasing the volume of code produced.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[2B  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m5. The Evolution of the De"]
[0.000, "o", "veloper Role\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                             \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mProductivity in this age is less about \"typing speed\" and more about:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                              \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mContinuous Learning:\u001b[22m Developers must shift focus toward becoming \"intimate with the business domain.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                           \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mBrainstorming and Experimentation:\u001b[22m Using agents to leverage \"massive experimentation\" (as noted in the DDD highlights) to find the right architectural patterns.\u001b[39m                      "]
