[0.068, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[1;1H\u001b[29B  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mProductivity in this age is less about \"typing speed\" and more about:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                              \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m▄\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mContinuous Learning:\u001b[22m Developers must shift focus toward becoming \"intimate with the business domain.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                           \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[14B\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;110;106;134m│\u001b[38;2;69;71;90m▀\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[38;2;110;106;134m╰────────────────────────────────────"]
[0.001, "o", "───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[39m \r\n\u001b[8B\u001b[52;4H\u001b[?2026l"]
[0.052, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[1;1H  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244msuck.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                              \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m*\u001b[39m \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244mArticle Angle:\u001b[22m Coding agents aren't just for writing functions; their greatest productivity impact may be as intelligent retrieval layers that solve the information discovery problem, allowing developers to bypass the\u001b[39m        \r\n     \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mfriction of navigating fragmented documentation and legacy codebases.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                            \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                 "]
[0.000, "o", "                     \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m2. Agents as Standardization Engines\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                                \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mYour notes on \"core concepts\" highlight that agents provide:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                        \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mDomain Expertise:\u001b[22m Specialized agents (Go, Security, DevOps) provide deep knowledge on demand.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                     "]
[0.000, "o", "               \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mTeam Standardization:\u001b[22m Using a \"senior reviewer\" agent ensures that every developer—regardless of experience—is measured against the same standards and best practices.\u001b[39m                                                           \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mConsistent Voice:\u001b[22m Reducing the cognitive load of switching between different styles or behavioral constraints.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[3"]
[0.000, "o", "8;2;224;222;244m3. Controlling Complexity with Domain-Driven Design (DDD)\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                           \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mThe complexity of modern software is still the greatest hurdle. As highlighted in your \u001b[3mDomain-Driven Design\u001b[23m notes:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                  \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mLeverage through Models:\u001b[22m LLMs can help developers brainstorm and experiment with domain models more rapidly.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                     \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m*\u001b[39m \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244mConscious Knowledge Growth:\u001b[22m Highly productive teams grow their knowledge consciously. Agents can act as the \"memory\" of a team, distilling brainstorming sessions into a \"knowledge-r"]
[0.000, "o", "ich model\" that binds the domain to the\u001b[39m     \r\n     \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mcode.\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m4. Measuring What Matters (DORA Metrics)\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                  "]
[0.000, "o", "          \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mTo move beyond hype, productivity must be grounded in the \"science of delivery.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                    \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mArticle Angle:\u001b[22m Use DORA metrics (from \u001b[3mThe Why\u001b[23m) to evaluate if AI tools are actually moving the needle on velocity and stability, rather than just increasing the volume of code produced.\u001b[39m                                        \r\n\u001b[E                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244m5. The Evolution of the Developer Role\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                              "]
[0.000, "o", "                \r\n  \u001b[38;2;224;222;244mProductivity in this age is less about \"typing speed\" and more about:\u001b[39m                                                                                                                                                               \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mContinuous Learning:\u001b[22m Developers must shift focus toward becoming \"intimate with the business domain.\"\u001b[39m                                                                                                                            \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[1mBrainstorming and Experimentation:\u001b[22m Using agents to leverage \"massive experimentation\" (as noted in the DDD highlights) to find the right architectural patterns.\u001b[39m                                                                 \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "]
[0.000, "o", "          \r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;224;222;244mPotential Article Titles:\u001b[39m\u001b[22m                                                                                                                                                                                                           \r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[3mFrom Tech Debt to Information Friction: How Agents are Rewriting the Productivity Playbook\u001b[39m\u001b[23m                                                                                                                                      \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[3mThe Senior Reviewer in the Machine: Standardizing Engineering Teams with AI\u001b[39m\u001b[23m                                                                                                                  "]
[0.000, "o", "                                   \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[38;2;224;222;244m* \u001b[3mModel-Driven Development in the Age of Agents: Using LLMs to Conquer Complexity\u001b[39m\u001b[23m                                                                                                                                                 \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \u001b[38;2;69;71;90m█\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[48;2;32;30;44m\u001b[38;2;25;23;36m▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀"]
